#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn11.17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn11.17:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 11 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 11 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 17. Buddhavandanāsutta → vandanāsuttaṃ (bj) | vandanasuttaṃ (s1-3) | vandanā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn11.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Buddhavandanāsutta "
msgstr "17. Homage to the Buddha "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn11.17:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ jetavane. "
msgstr "Near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.17:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā divāvihāragato hoti paṭisallīno. "
msgstr "Now at that time the Buddha had gone into retreat for the day’s meditation. "

msgctxt "sn11.17:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho sakko ca devānamindo brahmā ca sahampati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā paccekaṃ dvārabāhaṃ nissāya aṭṭhaṃsu. "
msgstr "Then Sakka, lord of gods, and Brahmā Sahampati approached the Buddha and stationed themselves one by each door-post. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn11.17:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho sakko devānamindo bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: "
msgstr "Then Sakka recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn11.17:2.1"
msgid "“Uṭṭhehi vīra vijitasaṅgāma, "
msgstr "“Rise, hero! Victor in battle, with burden put down, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.17:2.2"
msgid "Pannabhāra anaṇa vicara loke; "
msgstr "wander the world without obligation. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.17:2.3"
msgid "Cittañca te suvimuttaṃ, "
msgstr "Your mind is fully liberated, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.17:2.4"
msgid "Cando yathā pannarasāya rattin”ti. "
msgstr "like the moon on the fifteenth night.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.234, sc3
msgctxt "sn11.17:3.1"
msgid "“Na kho, devānaminda, tathāgatā evaṃ vanditabbā. "
msgstr "“Lord of gods, that’s not how to pay homage to the Realized Ones. "

msgctxt "sn11.17:3.2"
msgid "Evañca kho, devānaminda, tathāgatā vanditabbā: "
msgstr "This is how it should be done: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.502, sc4
msgctxt "sn11.17:4.1"
msgid "‘Uṭṭhehi vīra vijitasaṅgāma, "
msgstr "‘Rise, hero! Victor in battle, leader of the caravan, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.17:4.2"
msgid "Satthavāha anaṇa vicara loke; "
msgstr "wander the world without obligation. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.17:4.3"
msgid "Desassu bhagavā dhammaṃ, "
msgstr "Let the Blessed One teach the Dhamma! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn11.17:4.4"
msgid "Aññātāro bhavissantī’”ti. "
msgstr "There will be those who understand!’”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
